                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "z_interface_full_column",
                    "description": "Verifies Oleson Eq. 4.7 interface-depth recurrence across all 16 interfaces: surface z_interface_1 = 0, interior z_interface_{i+1} = 0.5 * (z_node_i + z_node_{i+1}) for i = 1..14, and bottom z_interface_16 = z_node_15 + 0.5 * dz_layer_15. For a uniform grid the interior interfaces fall at integer multiples of dz_total / N = 0.02 m and the bottom interface equals dz_total = 0.3 m (matches upstream `roof_wall_road_snow_temperatures_test.jl:951` bottom-interface check at dz_total). Anchors the interface positions used for inter-layer thermal-conductivity coupling.",
